ss="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US">33.1</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="396"><p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>高中</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width="160"><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US">2.0</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="396"><p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span>大专及以上</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width="160"><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US">0.1</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><b><span lang="EN-US">3</span></b><b>、农业技术人员</b><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span lang="EN-US">2006</span><span>年末，全市共有农业技术人员<span lang="EN-US">9800</span>人，其中，在农业生产经营单位中从业<span lang="EN-US">4696</span>人。按职称分，高、中、初级农业技术人员分别为<span lang="EN-US">344</span>人、<span lang="EN-US">2000</span>人和<span lang="EN-US">7456</span>人。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b>表<span lang="EN-US">3&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>农业技术人员数量</b><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="right" style="text-align: right;"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>单位：人</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p><div align="center"><table class="MsoNormalTable layui-table" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0"><tbody><tr><td width="243"><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center;"><span>　</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width="130"><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center;"><span>达州市</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width="138"><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center;"><font size="3">比重<span lang="EN-US">%<o:p></o:p></span></font></p></td></tr><tr><td width="243"><p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span>合计</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width="130"><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US">9800</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width="138"><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US"><font size="3">100<o:p></o:p></font></span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="243"><p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span>初级</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width="130"><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US">7456</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width="138"><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US"><font size="3">76.1<o:p></o:p></font></span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="243"><p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span>中级</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width="130"><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US">2000</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width="138"><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US"><font size="3">20.4<o:p></o:p></font></span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="243"><p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span>高级</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width="130"><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US">344</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width="138"><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US"><font size="3">3.5<o:p></o:p></font></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><b><span lang="EN-US">4</span></b><b>、设施农业</b><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span lang="EN-US">2006</span><span>年末，全市温室面积<span lang="EN-US">18.1</span>公顷，大棚面积<span lang="EN-US">46.3</span>公顷，农业生产用房面积<span lang="EN-US">2851.3</span>万平方米。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><b><span lang="EN-US">5</span></b><b>、耕地承包、经营与流转</b><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span lang="EN-US">2006</span><span>年全市从户籍所在村集体承包有耕地的农村常住户<span lang="EN-US">104</span>万户，占本地户数的<span lang="EN-US">99.4%</span>；有经营耕地的农户<span lang="EN-US">100</span>万户，占本地户数的<span lang="EN-US">96%</span>；有<span lang="EN-US">5.4%</span>的农户将耕地租出、包出、转出；有<span lang="EN-US">37.9%</span>的农户将耕地租入、包入、转入。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span>三、农村基础设施建设和基本社会服务</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span>本次普查对全市<span lang="EN-US">311</span>个乡镇和<span lang="EN-US">2862</span>个行政村的基础设施建设和基本社会服务进行了调查。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><b><span lang="EN-US">1</span></b><b>、交通</b><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span lang="EN-US">2006</span><span>年末，在乡镇地域内有火车站的乡镇占全部乡镇的<span lang="EN-US">8.7%</span>，有码头的占<span lang="EN-US">13.5%</span>，有二级以上公路通过的占<span lang="EN-US">28.9%</span>。乡镇政府所在地距县城在一小时车程内的占<span lang="EN-US">48.9%</span>，距一级公路或高速公路出入口在<span lang="EN-US">50</span>公里之内的占<span lang="EN-US">43.1%</span>。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b>表<span lang="EN-US">4&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>有交通设施的乡镇比重</b><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="right" style="text-align: right;"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>单位：<span lang="EN-US">%</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p><div align="center"><table class="MsoNormalTable layui-table" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="568" border="0"><tbody><tr><td width="60%"><p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span>　</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width="39%"><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center;"><span>达州市</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="60%"><p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span>有火车站的乡镇</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width="39%"><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US">8.7</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="60%"><p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span>有码头的乡镇</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width="39%"><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US">13.5</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="60%"><p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span>有二级以上公路通过的乡镇</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width="39%"><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US">28.9</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="60%"><p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span>距一级公路或高速公路出入口在<st1:chmetcnv w:st="on" unitname="公里" sourcevalue="50" hasspace="False" negative="False" numbertype="1" tcsc="0"><span lang="EN-US">50</span>公里</st1:chmetcnv>之内的乡镇</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td width="39%"><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="EN-US">43.1</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></sp